Class ParametersManager

  • java.lang.Object

    public abstract class ParametersManager
extends Object
implements io.tessilab.oss.openutils.designpatterns.observer.ParametrizedObserver<ProcessResult>
    The abstract class that represents the class to provide the parameters to the ExecutionRun to be tested. What parameters give and when to give them are computed by this subclasses.
